Class SortedDoubleLinkedList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • BasicDoubleLinkedList<T>
      • SortedDoubleLinkedList<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of value in the sorted doubly linked list
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>

    public class SortedDoubleLinkedList<T>
extends BasicDoubleLinkedList<T>
    A generic sorted doubly-linked list will be constructed using a provided Comparator to determine how the list is to be sorted. It extends BasicDoubleLinkedList class. The addToFront and the addToEnd methods will not be supported and an add method will be added that inserts to the doubly-linked list in sorted order dependent on the Comparator.
    Author:
    Alex Juan
